title: Got Questions About Transferring to UCLA? Talk with the UCLA Peer Mentor on October 26 ...
text: ( Source : Los Angeles Valley College ) UCLA will have its Peer Mentor on-campus to answer your questions about transferring to UCLA on October 26 from 10 a.m.-2 p.m. at the Career / Transfer Center . Student can also schedule to meet one-on-one
